posts.raw_content:
Bye y'all! The Internet is impeding my walk with God so I must stop for a while or forever.

So let us pray 

Heavenly Father, I come boldly before Your Throne today, with praise and thanksgiving, all thanks to the glorious finished work of Your Son Jesus Christ, the King of kings and the Lord of lords, whose Name is above all others, and of whose Kingdom there shall be no end! 

God, Father, Abba, I cry out to you, won't you heal our sin sick land? Make of us a nation of kings and priests, sons and daughters of the Most High? For You have said 

>14 If my people, which are called by my name, shall humble themselves, and pray, and seek my face, and turn from their wicked ways; then will I hear from heaven, and will forgive their sin, and will heal their land.

Grant us a MIGHTY end times outpouring of Your Holy Spirit, as you promised in Joel and Acts 

>17 And it shall come to pass in the last days, saith God, I will pour out of my Spirit upon all flesh: and your sons and your daughters shall prophesy, and your young men shall see visions, and your old men shall dream dreams:

>18 And on my servants and on my handmaidens I will pour out in those days of my Spirit; and they shall prophesy:

I pray for Holy Spirit boldness and anointing that we all may proclaim Your Holy Word to the uttermost part of the earth, and that BILLIONS would come to a saving knowledge of Christ Jesus. 

Heavenly Father I ask for blessings so abundant and healing so miraculous upon the TD crew that all would know that You are God. Bless and protect our president. Grant him strength, love, and wisdom to rule. In Jesus Name I declare a mighty hedge of protection around him and his supporters. In Jesus Name I loose legions of ministering angels from the realms of glory to guard him and our nation. In Jesus Name I bind the enemy and cast him into outer darkness. 

In Jesus' glorious and conquering Name I pray
